ss on the necessity of\nrescaling the virial mass in simulations when comparing with analytical\napproaches on the ground of the matter not accounted as part of the halos and\nthe halo mass limit due to numerical. Our analysis supports the presence of a\ndiffuse dark matter component that is not taken into account in the measured\nhalo MFs inasmuch as it is not part of the collapsed structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2013 20:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Sep 2013 00:29:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-10"}
