provides a viable pathway\nof forming high-mass black holes at early cosmic times.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Apr 2013 14:15:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 May 2013 17:11:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
